== BySHBrowser

Small file-browser application with easy file sharing and zipping/unzipping features. Created for ByteSized-Hosting.com.

=== Milestone 1 - features

* Browse folders
* Download files
* Zip files / folders in the background
* Share files via unique urls (no login required)
* Multiple user support

